\c 45
\s UJosefa uyaziveza kubafowabo
\p
\v 1 UJosefa-ke wayengelakuzibamba\x + 43.31. Esta 5.10. Isa. 42.14; 63.15; 64.12. 1 Sam. 13.12.\x* phambi kwabo ababemi laye, wamemeza \add wathi\add*: Khuphani wonke umuntu asuke kimi. Futhi kwakungelamuntu owayemi laye lapho uJosefa eziveza kubafowabo.
\v 2 Wasephakamisa ilizwi lakhe ngokukhala, aze ezwa amaGibithe lendlu kaFaro yezwa.
\v 3 UJosefa wasesithi kubafowabo: NginguJosefa\x + Seb. 7.13.\x*. Ubaba usaphila yini? Kodwa abafowabo kabaze bamphendula, ngoba besanganisekile phambi kwakhe.
\v 4 UJosefa wasesithi kubafowabo: Ake lisondele kimi. Basondela-ke. Wasesithi: NginguJosefa umfowenu elamthengisela iGibithe.
\v 5 Khathesi-ke, lingadabuki, lingazithukutheleli\f + \fk lingazithukutheleli: \fl Heb. \fq kakungabi lentukuthelo emehlweni enu.\f*, ukuthi langithengisa lapha, ngoba uNkulunkulu wangithuma phambi kwenu ukulondoloza impilo\x + 50.20. Hlab. 105.16,17.\x*.
\v 6 Ngoba liminyaka emibili indlala iphakathi kwelizwe; njalo kuseleminyaka emihlanu okungayikulinywa kuvunwe ngayo.
\v 7 Njalo uNkulunkulu wangithuma phambi kwenu ukulimisela insali emhlabeni, lokuligcina liphila ngokukhulula okukhulu.
\v 8 Khathesi-ke, lina alingithumelanga lapha, kodwa uNkulunkulu; wasengimisa ngaba nguyise kaFaro\x + 45.26; 41.43.\x*, lenkosi yendlu yakhe yonke, lombusi elizweni lonke leGibithe.
\v 9 Phangisani lenyukele kubaba, lithi kuye: Itsho njalo indodana yakho uJosefa: UNkulunkulu ungimise inkosi yeGibithe lonke; yehlela kimi, ungaphuzi;
\v 10 uzahlala elizweni leGosheni\x + 46.28,29,34; 47.1,4,6,27; 50.8; 47.11.\x*, ube seduze lami, wena labantwana bakho labantwana babantwabakho, lezimvu zakho lenkomo zakho, lakho konke olakho.
\v 11 Njalo ngizakondla lapho, ngoba isekhona iminyaka emihlanu yendlala, hlezi ube ngumyanga, wena lendlu yakho lakho konke olakho\x + Zaga 20.13; 23.21; 30.9.\x*.
\v 12 Khangelani-ke, amehlo enu ayabona, lamehlo omfowethu uBenjamini, ukuthi umlomo wami ukhuluma kini.
\v 13 Bikelani ubaba lonke udumo lwami eGibithe, lakho konke elikubonileyo, liphangise lehlisele ubaba lapha\x + Seb. 7.14.\x*.
\v 14 Wasewela entanyeni kaBenjamini umfowabo, wakhala inyembezi; loBenjamini wakhala inyembezi entanyeni yakhe.
\v 15 Wasebanga bonke abafowabo, wakhala inyembezi phezu kwabo. Njalo emva kwalokhu abafowabo baxoxa laye.
\p
\v 16 Kwathi lelilizwi lizwakala endlini kaFaro lisithi, abafowabo bakaJosefa bafikile, kwaba kuhle emehlweni kaFaro lemehlweni enceku zakhe.
\v 17 UFaro wasesithi kuJosefa: Tshela abafowenu \add uthi\add*: Yenzani lokhu, yethwesani inyamazana zenu, lihambe liye elizweni leKhanani,
\v 18 lithathe uyihlo lemizi yenu, libuye kimi; besengilinika okuhle kwelizwe leGibithe, beselisidla amanono elizwe\x + Nani 18.12,29.\x*.
\v 19 Wena-ke usulayiwe; yenzani lokhu, zithatheleni elizweni leGibithe izinqola zabantwanyana benu labomkenu, lithwale uyihlo libuye.
\v 20 Futhi ilihlo lenu lingakhathaleli impahla zenu, ngoba okuhle kwelizwe lonke leGibithe kungokwenu.
\v 21 Asesenza njalo amadodana kaIsrayeli; uJosefa wasewanika izinqola njengokulaya\f + \fk ukulaya: \fl Heb. \fq umlomo.\f* kukaFaro, wabanika umphako wendlela.
\v 22 Wabanika bonke, kwaba ngulowo lalowo izembatho zokuntshintsha\x + 2 Kho. 5.5,23.\x*; kodwa uBenjamini wamnika inhlamvu zesiliva ezingamakhulu amathathu, lezembatho zokuntshintsha ezinhlanu\x + 43.34.\x*.
\v 23 Wasethumela kuyise kanje, obabhemi abalitshumi, bethwele okwezinto ezinhle zeGibithe, labobabhemikazi abalitshumi bethwele amabele lezinkwa lokudla kwendlela kukayise\x + 2 Lan. 11.23. Dan. 4.12,21.\x*.
\v 24 Wasebathuma abafowabo bahamba. Wathi kibo: Lingaxabani endleleni\x + Hlab. 4.4; Efe. 4.26. Zaga 29.9. Hez. 16.43.\x*.
\p
\v 25 Basebesenyuka besuka eGibithe, bafika elizweni leKhanani, kuJakobe uyise.
\v 26 Bambikela besithi: UJosefa usaphila, njalo ungumbusi elizweni leGibithe lonke. Inhliziyo yakhe yasiphela amandla, ngoba wayengabakholwa.
\v 27 Basebemtshela wonke amazwi kaJosefa ayewatshilo kibo. Kwathi esezibonile izinqola uJosefa ayezithume ukumthwala\x + 45.19,21; 46.5. Nani 7.3,6.\x*, umoya kaJakobe uyise wavuseleka.
\v 28 UIsrayeli wasesithi: Kwenele, uJosefa indodana yami usaphila; ngizahamba ngimbone ngingakafi.
